---
import coaching from "../karen-coaching.jpg";
import Scroll from "../layouts/Scroll.astro";

let underlineGradient = "bg-gradient-to-r from-orange_gradient_start to-orange_gradient_finish bg-no-repeat bg-[length:100%_8px] bg-bottom pb-2"
---

<div class="flex items-center justify-center">
  <div class="h-screen text-left">
    <div>
      <h1
        class= `font-bold text-6xl order-1 mt-3 ml-3 z-20 w-fit ${underlineGradient}`
      >
      Coaching Intro
    </h1>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2">
      <div class="flex-grow ml-3 mt-4 pt-4">
        <p>
          As a coach, my mission is to help you shine and achieve your full
          potential. Whether you're facing a new challenge at work, stepping
          into a leadership role, seeking a promotion, or exploring a new
          direction, I'm here to support you on your journey.
          <br /><br />
          Coaching is a transformative process, one that aims to guide you from where
          you are now to where you aspire to be. Drawing from the principles of sports
          coaching, I'll work with you to enhance self-awareness, clarify your goals,
          and bridge the gap between potential and success.
          <br /><br />
          Our one-on-one sessions will focus on understanding your values and experiences,
          and creating a pathway to achieve your personal goals. As we collaborate,
          I'll encourage you to remain motivated, engaged, and open to the possibilities
          that coaching brings.
          <br /><br />
          Together, we can unlock your best self.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex-grow ml-3 pl-14 pt-4 mt-3">
        <img src={coaching} alt="karen coaching" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <Scroll srollTo="#getInTouch" text="scroll to explore coaching packages"/>
  </div>
</div>

